---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="McGennis Family Businesses - Jefferson City, Missouri Entrepreneurs"
  description="Explore BXP, The Honey Homestead, and more businesses founded by Caleb McGennis in Jefferson City, Missouri. Innovation meets entrepreneurship."
>
  <section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-32 px-4 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Our Business Ventures
      </h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-500 font-light">
        Building diverse businesses and creating value in Jefferson City and beyond
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
          Founded and operated by <a href="/family/caleb" class="text-mcgennis-navy font-medium hover:text-mcgennis-gold transition">Caleb Michael McGennis</a>,
          these businesses represent innovation, quality, and commitment to excellence in Central Missouri.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- BXP -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-mcgennis-navy">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-mcgennis-navy group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">BXP</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-500">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">
              Technology & Innovation
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              BXP leads the way in technology solutions and innovation services. We provide cutting-edge solutions
              for businesses looking to modernize and scale their operations in the digital age.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <span class="inline-block bg-mcgennis-navy text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">
                Technology
              </span>
              <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium ml-2">
                Innovation
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Honey Homestead -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-mcgennis-gold">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-mcgennis-gold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">The Honey Homestead</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-500">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">
              Agriculture & Natural Products
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              The Honey Homestead produces premium natural honey and homestead products. We're committed to sustainable
              practices and delivering pure, high-quality products to Jefferson City and surrounding communities.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <span class="inline-block bg-brass-button brightness-110 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">
                Natural Products
              </span>
              <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium ml-2">
                Sustainable
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What's the Process for -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-mcgennis-forest">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-mcgennis-forest group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">What's the Process for</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-500">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">
              Process Management & Documentation
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Simplifying complex processes and making procedures accessible to everyone. We help businesses and
              individuals understand and document workflows, making operations more efficient and transparent.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <span class="inline-block bg-mcgennis-forest text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">
                Process Management
              </span>
              <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium ml-2">
                Documentation
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Toxic Tournaments -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-mcgennis-maroon">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-mcgennis-maroon group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Toxic Tournaments</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-500">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">
              Esports & Gaming Events
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Organizing competitive gaming tournaments and esports events. Bringing together the gaming community
              in Jefferson City and Missouri for exciting competitions and community building.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <span class="inline-block bg-mcgennis-maroon text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">
                Esports
              </span>
              <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium ml-2">
                Gaming
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Nostalgia Nuke -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-mcgennis-navy">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-mcgennis-navy group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M7 4v16M17 4v16M3 8h4m10 0h4M3 12h18M3 16h4m10 0h4M4 20h16a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a1 1 0 00-1 1v14a1 1 0 001 1z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Nostalgia Nuke</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-500">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">
              Retro Gaming & Content Creation
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Celebrating retro gaming culture and creating nostalgic content. We bring back the magic of classic
              games and memories, connecting generations through shared gaming experiences.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm italic text-mcgennis-navy pt-3 border-t border-gray-200">
              "For by him all things were created, in heaven and on earth, visible and invisible, whether thrones or dominions or rulers or authorities—all things were created through him and for him." — Colossians 1:16
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <span class="inline-block bg-mcgennis-navy text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">
                Retro Gaming
              </span>
              <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium ml-2">
                Content
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- LoHP -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-mcgennis-gold">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-mcgennis-gold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">LoHP</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-500">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">
              League of Honorable Players
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              LoHP (League of Honorable Players) is a competitive esports team building community through honorable gameplay.
              We combine competitive excellence with character development, proving that winning and integrity go hand in hand.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <span class="inline-block bg-brass-button brightness-110 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">
                Esports
              </span>
              <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium ml-2">
                Community
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder Section -->
  <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-white p-10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
          <div>
            <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-mcgennis-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
              Meet The Founder
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-4 font-light">
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Caleb Michael McGennis</strong> (dr4g0nbyt3) is the entrepreneurial force behind these ventures.
              With years of experience in technology, ministry, and business development, Caleb brings innovation
              and excellence to every project.
            </p>
            <a href="/family/caleb" class="group inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-mcgennis-navy text-white font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
              Learn More About Caleb
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 px-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Interested In Working Together?</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-brass-horizontal rounded-full shadow-sm mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-gray-500 font-light">
        Reach out to discuss partnerships, collaborations, or learn more about our businesses
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-brass-button brightness-110 text-white font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
        Contact Us
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEO Content -->
  <section class="sr-only">
    <h2>McGennis Family Businesses in Jefferson City, Missouri</h2>
    <p>
      Caleb Michael McGennis operates multiple successful businesses in Jefferson City, Missouri and beyond.
      His ventures include BXP (technology and innovation), The Honey Homestead (natural honey and homestead products),
      What's the Process for (process management), Toxic Tournaments (esports), Nostalgia Nuke (retro gaming content),
      and LoHP / League of Honorable Players (competitive esports team).
    </p>
    <p>
      Keywords: Jefferson City businesses, Missouri entrepreneurs, Caleb McGennis businesses, BXP Jefferson City,
      The Honey Homestead Missouri, Toxic Tournaments esports, Jefferson City startups, Missouri business owners,
      dr4g0nbyt3 businesses, McGennis family enterprises
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
